<title>O LOVE, THAT WILL NOT LET ME GO</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw lungsiet, ei nusieh lo ding,
 Ka tha chau Nangah ka chawlhsak;
 Hinna ka bat ka hun pie kit,
 Na tuipi thukah luong ina;
 Tamzaw, dimzaw'n luong hen.

[V2]
 2. Aw Vak ka lampi cheng salhvak,
 Kei meisel mit kuon ka hun piei;
 Na vakna ka lungah a vak,
 Na ni Vak achun nicheng in;
 Vakzaw, hawih zaw'n um hen.

[V3]
 3. Nawpna, mun haksaa ei hawl,
 Lunggil in ka hun ngilhthei puoi;
 Guoh laka nigui vak bangin,
 Na thutiem zuoulo tih ka hei;
 Ziechun mitthi hul ding.

[V4]
 4. Aw Kross, nang ka luchang dawmkang,
 Nang apat ka taimang ngam puoi;
 Damsung lopina thihsak ka,
 Tichun pakcha banga hingin
 Hinna tawplo nei ka.</lyrics>
</song>